VIM CHEATSHEET NAJS FINGS

zz - Center screen on the thing on cursor
zb - show lines over the thing on cursor
zt - show lines under the thing on cursor
*/& - get to next/prev occurence of word under
m<register letter> - make a mark
`<letter> - go to mark
'<letter> - go to first char in marks line
"<letter> + d/y/whatever - delete/yank/whatever into the register

INSERT MODE
CTRL_r + register - paste text
CTRL_a - paste text in . register

vim surround
cs([ - replace '(' with '['
ysiw] - wrap word with '[]' no spaces
ysiw[ - wrap word with '[]' spaces
yss) - wrap whole line
ds( - unwrap

unimpaired vim
[e/]e - switch line with the line on top/bottom
[b/]b - next/prev buffer
[l/]l - next/prev linter bitching
[u/]u - urlencode/urldecode
you - toggle 'cursorcolumn'
=p - paste with reindent
[<space>/[<space> - add empty line after/before cursor

vim-rails
:help rails
CTRL-W_f - open thing under cursor in new split
CTRL-W_gf - open thing under cursor in new tab
:Clog <env> - log file for environment
:Preview! - open current path for file in netrw

rubymotion
text objects
am - whole method
im - method body

dispatch
:Copen - open buffer with latest output from tasks run via :Rails, etc.
maps
m<CR>                   |:Make|<CR>
m<Space>                |:Make|<Space>
m!                      |:Make|!
m?                      Show 'makeprg'
`<CR>                   |:Dispatch|<CR>
`<Space>                |:Dispatch|<Space>
`!                      |:Dispatch|!
`?                      |:FocusDispatch|<CR>
'<CR>                   |:Start|<CR>
'<Space>                |:Start|<Space>
'!                      |:Start|!
'?                      Show |b:start|
g'<CR>                  |:Spawn|<CR>
g'<Space>               |:Spawn|<Space>
g'!                     |:Spawn|!
g'?                     Show 'shell'

CALENDAR
:Calendar -split=vertical

vim-fugitive
:Gcgrep - git grep

ctrlp
<c-d> - toggle filename/full path search
<c-r> - toggle regexp search
<c-b> + <c-f> - scroll search modes
